-attachment-3786199" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3786199" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="2023 年诺丁山狂欢节。照片来源：HENRY NICHOLLS/AFP via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3786199" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年诺丁山狂欢节。照片来源：HENRY NICHOLLS/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>大卫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/craig-david-announces-commitment-2025-uk-arena-tour-with-lemar-buy-tickets-3751629">最近宣布了 2025 年的巡演</a>。门票现已发售 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcraig-david-tickets%2Fartist%2F703676" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买</a>。</p><p>演出日期从 2 月 2 日（星期日）开始，以利兹 First Direct Arena 的开幕之夜拉开帷幕，然后两晚后（2 月 4 日）在格拉斯哥的 Armadillo 场地继续演出。</p><p>从那里开始，本月剩余时间里，纽卡斯尔、米尔顿凯恩斯、布莱顿、卡迪夫和诺丁汉的演出将在曼彻斯特的 Co-Op Live 竞技场、伯明翰名胜世界竞技场、伯恩茅斯国际中心等地结束。最后是 2 月 20 日在伦敦举办的 The O2。</p><p>